Privacy Policy – North America
Last Update: January 2022
This privacy policy applies if you reside in Canada or the US.  If you reside
                      elsewhere, please review this other version instead.
Peggy Inc. (“
Peggy
”) brings together Galleries,
                      Artists, Collectors and other stakeholders in the art ecosystem (collectively, our “
Users
”) to make living with and investing in art accessible to
                      all.
Peggy values and respects your privacy. We have prepared this privacy policy to explain the manner
                      in which we collect, use and disclose personal information through our website located at Peggy.com (the
                      “
Website
”), through any mobile device software provided by us to
                      you (the “
App
”), and in our other interactions with you
                      (collectively, the “
Service
”).  By using our
                      Service, you consent to our collection and other handling of personal information as described in this privacy
                      policy.
